It apparently had a huge shell for

It lives in shallow tidal pools.

shielded with a sturdy shell. There
are traces of it left in its cells.

it oozes purple fluid and escapes.

 lil nu. On ne sait toujours pas pourquoi il a
quitt locan au profit de la terre ferme.

Es ernhrt sich hauptschlich von Plankton,
das man mit bloem Auge nicht sehen kann.
Es ist noch unklar, warum es an Land kommt.

Su principal alimento es plancton invisible. Sale

Si nutre principalmente di plancton.
A volte si sposta sulla terraferma per motivi

Plankton, invisible to the naked eye, is its main
food source. It comes onto the land periodically,
but the reason for this is not known.

Their shape and color change, depending on
their environment and diet. There are many of

Il peut rejoindre la terre ferme pour chercher

Il scrte un liquide mauve pour intimider

Es stt ein lila Sekret aus, mit dem es seine

Puede desplazarse tambin por tierra firme en
pos de su presa. Deja tras de s, entonces, el

Segrega un lquido morado para intimidar a sus

Pu salire sulla terraferma in cerca di cibo.
Quando si sposta, lascia dietro di s una scia

It secretes a purple fluid to deter enemies.
This fluid isnt poisonousinstead, its super
sticky, and once it sticks, its very hard to unstick.

Its search for food sometimes leads it onto land,
where it leaves behind a sticky trail of slime as it

Aunque blando, su cuerpo es tremendamente

Lo recubre una sustancia viscosa. Se resiente

permanecer mucho tiempo en tierra firme.

Il suo corpo molliccio  in grado di assorbire

resistente.

ricoperto da un liquido viscido. Non pu

Its body is covered in a sticky slime. Its very
susceptible to dehydration, so it cant spend

The softness of its body helps disperse the force
